ái bí ẩn Kim Yi Seol (Lee Yi Dam), “tiểu tam” xen vào hôn nhân giữa Yoon Jae Hee và Jung Joon Hyeok.</p>","tmdb_id":138947,"cast":["Soo Ae","Kim Kang-woo","Kim Mi-sook","Lee E-dam","Lee Hak-ju","Kim Joo-ryoung","Kim Young-jae","Kim Ji-hyun","Baek Ji-won","Nam Kee-ae","Park Ji-il","Nam Moon-chul","Yum Dong-hun","Seo Yi-an"],"director":["Jeon Chang-geun"],"keywords":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Soo Ae","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Soo Ae","tmdb_id":1299358,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ycwBQ9W2d6GWRIgbj4pzfq2J6bg.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1299358"},{"name":"Kim Kang-woo","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kim Kang-woo","tmdb_id":84751,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1B883y0AG0WPTmGkC14XIggXVLz.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/84751"},{"name":"Kim Mi-sook","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kim Mi-sook","tmdb_id":92678,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cRq8LIJTFsMaiIk54aoCscWHtqA.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/92678"},{"name":"Lee E-dam","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Lee E-dam","tmdb_id":3314352,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/raND8efeLH0TmIgs6ZSzgp42the.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3314352"},{"name":"Lee Hak-ju","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Lee Hak-ju","tmdb_id":1615316,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3NgAXgOlZyS3y7tD0EcnCSSNc9E.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1615316"},{"name":"Kim Joo-ryoung","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kim Joo-ryoung","tmdb_id":587677,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cX9AefszYLxAKbPlrIRRCABY87b.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/587677"},{"name":"Kim Young-jae","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kim Young-jae","tmdb_id":135850,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wSgDPw6fSGgrwJLO0QaITbS758L.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/135850"},{"name":"Kim Ji-hyun","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kim Ji-hyun","tmdb_id":2183220,"profile":"https://image.tmdb